    because so that we can remove the last 
    guess using the undoInput() method

    Stored in form:
    LinkedHashmap<guess, encrypted>
end note

note left of Cryptogram::correctMappings
    Stored in form:
    LinkedHashmap<correct, encrypted>
end note

